recycle overlays:

to left of ship:   cancel(rename) mode 99c (IF CANCEL MODE DOESNT WORK >> RESET CORE CRUSHER)
to right of ship:  special weapon mode 99c

below cancel mode:    ship power
right of ship power:  shield power
left of new weapon:   laser power
below special weapon: NOVA SPLITTER

below each of these 4 except NOVA SPLITTER is a % ranging from 10 to 100%, split by 18%.
once the 5th upgrade is installed, tapping will cycle by 18% to 100%, 10%
colored circle below each in the overlay

NOVA SPLITTER installs NOVA SPLITTER into weapon arsenal
once maxed, LIMIT DISMANTLER, LIMIT __WEAPONNAME__ up to FULL ARMORY

cost is shown beneath each of these 4 with a NUMBER # then a big fill colored circle O

this big O fills up when the player collets 54 debris cores

show 0 Cores at start.
show 4 core spendable upgrades at start.

twitter, email, sms, facebook up top below title

below twitter: DEADLINE ACTIVE to DEADLINE STALLED
below facebook: SCANNER OFF to SHOT PREDICTION

MODE upgrades do not appear without 20 plays (or at least 2 core cycles)
DEADLINE/SCANNER do not appear without 10 playes (or at least 1 core cycle)

